# overlay/patches/series — quilt-style ordered patch list (Debian 3.0(quilt) pattern).
#
# Each line is a unified diff under overlay/patches/, applied in order against the
# pinned pristine sources (nix/sources.json) during the build, with --check first:
# a failed hunk is a HARD ERROR, never a silent skip (the current build.sh has 93
# log_warn skips — that hazard is what this file removes).
#
# Populated in Phase 3 by nix/gen-patches.sh, which runs each legacy apply_* from
# scripts/build.sh against the pinned source and captures the resulting diff.
# Until then this list is empty and the legacy build.sh remains authoritative.
#
# Grouping (apply order): game(Balatro) → Steamodded → Cryptid → Amulet → others.
